c: 35
v: 37
t: "Therein, they will cry loudly (for help): \"Our Lord! Take us out (of here): We shall work good deeds and righteousness, not the (things) we used to do!\"— (Their answer from Allah will be:) \"Did We not give you (a) life long enough so that, he who would (have listened), was warned? And (moreover) the warner came to you. So you taste (the rewards for your deeds): For the wrongdoers there is no helper"